videos.description: RJ Barrett knocks down his second 3-pointer of the game against San Diego State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Barrett pulls up for early 3) 2018/11/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Barrett pulls up for early 3

videos.description: Duke forward Jack White drains a three from the corner extending the Blue Devils' lead and their bench loves it.
videos.headline: White knocks down corner 3

videos.description: Tre Jones crosses up a San Diego State defender and finishes through contact for an and-1.
videos.headline: Jones finishes an acrobatic and-1 in traffic

videos.description: RJ Barrett continues to dominate as he drains a deep pull-up 3 to extend Duke's lead over San Diego State.
videos.headline: Barrett drains pull-up 3, drops 16 in 1st half

videos.description: San Diego State is chipping at Duke's lead, as Jalen McDaniels finishes a tough layup with contact for an and-1.
videos.headline: McDaniels finishes tough layup for and-1

videos.description: Zion Williamson muscles his way through Aztec defenders for an easy and-1 finish.
videos.headline: Williamson shrugs off defender for and-1 finish

videos.description: Cam Reddish drives to the basket flings up a circus shot for an and-1 finish.
videos.headline: Reddish makes circus shot for and-1 finish

videos.description: Zion Williamson elevates for a jaw-dropping windmill dunk with authority.
videos.headline: Zion breaks off incredible windmill hammer

videos.description: RJ Barrett leads all scorers with 20 points while Cam Reddish and Zion Williamson combine for 29 more in Duke's 90-64 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Barrett, Reddish, Williamson propel Duke to easy win) 2018/11/19 ESHEET SOTFull

videos.headline: Barrett, Reddish, Williamson propel Duke to easy win

videos.description: Zion Williamson steals an inbounds pass and takes it the other way for an emphatic windmill slam against San Diego State.
